details.product_descriptions: Designed as the ultimate audio upgrade for the Harley Davidson 2015+ Road Glide the ARC Audio MPAK 12 is as extreme as you would ever need in a simple plug and play solution for your HD Road Glide Motorcycle. Exclusively by ARC Audio for the HD 2014+ Road glide motorcycles the MPAK12 is a complete upgrade solution that gives you everything you need to install it correctly into your HD motorcycle. Snuggled discretely beneath the factory radio in the stock boom audio amplifier location the MPAK12 Kit's Moto 600.4 amplifier finds its home without the need of any cutting, complex warranty voiding brackets or costly custom fabrication. The M.P.A.K.12 Kits include the ARC Audio Moto600.4 high power amplifier and upgraded HD Power kit that is required to handle the Moto 600.4's higher power levels safely.

details.product_descriptions: NS12v6-D1 | Sundown Audio 12' 3000W RMS Subwoofer FEATURES:  Size: This 12' model fits perfectly into your audio system and installation space, offering powerful sound without compromise. Power Handling: The Nightshade v.6 is built to handle extreme power levels with a power handling capacity of 3000W RMS. This makes it an excellent choice for high-powered audio systems that demand more. Improved Heat Dissipation: The Nightshade v.6 features fully functional cast aluminum heat-sinking that surrounds the entire motor, significantly enhancing long-term heat dissipation and ensuring optimal performance during extended high-power output sessions. Efficient Motor Venting: The Nightshade v.6 introduces a more efficient layout for motor venting, incorporating vertical slits for better heat management and overall performance. Voice Coil: This subwoofer features a 3' dual voice coil, contributing to its high power handling capacity and superior sound quality. Magnet Structure: The Nightshade v.6 utilizes a triple stack magnet, which helps to produce a powerful and accurate bass response. Suspension Design: The Nightshade v.6 features a high excursion suspension design, allowing the subwoofer to move more air and produce a deeper and more powerful bass response. Enclosure Compatibility: The Nightshade v.6 is designed to work well in both sealed and ported enclosures, offering flexibility in installation options. SPECIFICATIONS:  Subwoofer Cutout: 11.09'Subwoofer DEPTH: 12'
